com.simpligility.maven.plugins.android

Class AndroidTestRunListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simpligility.maven.plugins.android.AndroidTestRunListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.android.ddmlib.testrunner.ITestRunListener

    public class AndroidTestRunListener
extends Object
implements com.android.ddmlib.testrunner.ITestRunListener
    AndroidTestRunListener produces a nice output for the log for the test run as well as an xml file compatible with the junit xml report file format understood by many tools. It will do so for each device/emulator the tests run on.
